  "detailed_description": "<h1>Digital Deluxe Edition</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235750/extras/1d84d2c338d01cf143579b65823876b5.avif?t=1734646876\" width=180 height=220 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235750/extras/a58363fb42490d166a4f75744ce0f98a.avif?t=1734646876\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235750/extras/db3a82bd5a3578dadb042f1c4bd5b767.avif?t=1734646876\" width=220 height=220 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>You will not just play but you'll live the story of three youtubers</strong> after revealing to the world on national television that the clown Amendoim had a dangerous spirit incarnated within. These Three Youtubers decide to rest and take a vacation at the campsite but to their surprise bizarre things are happening and supernatural events want their soul embodied a dull spirit in all.<br><br>Just like the series and the movie this is the <strong> first game that mixes horror and comedy</strong>, blood and jokes<br><strong>Get crazy playing this game!...</strong><br><br>explore many different types of scenery and environments<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235750/extras/29e9d490ca3731176ceeb7c0aa8649fd.avif?t=1734646876\" width=566 height=272 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235750/extras/9e35c7bc4e3495501438861daeecca66.avif?t=1734646876\" width=566 height=272 /></span><br><br>fight zombies, spirits and the evil spirit itself<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235750/extras/6401e661c87ee07286e5ede8e2440dcb.avif?t=1734646876\" width=566 height=272 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235750/extras/7638853b6686d50a0abe724d33cbadff.avif?t=1734646876\" width=566 height=272 /></span><br><br>You can choose to play with three characters with different gameplay and personalities. And how about taking a really crazy test drive<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235750/extras/055a5b32ee8f1e36219a272e3f968b61.avif?t=1734646876\" width=566 height=272 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235750/extras/59545fbc0c350a6cbd8ffcc0a608a033.avif?t=1734646876\" width=566 height=272 /></span><br><br>Third person game. Three guys with different types of trinkets that shoot.<br>you can also use sniper trinkets or even use melee weapons to end the spirits<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235750/extras/36a42afeb84cacf46a040a38e8ac31e7.avif?t=1734646876\" width=566 height=272 /></span>",
